metadata.name: LOVE THIS 4 US #1/77
metadata.description:
LOVE THIS 4 US is an engaging genre-blending EP from multidisciplinary artist, KLOU. This introductory EP is a masterclass on the future of diverse artistry with it's range of hip-hop, pop, R&B, and dance it transcends singular genre ideals to showcase the vibiest artist in Web3.

Welcome to the first LOUNRTRIBE DROP!  
Link to site: lovethis4us.xyz  
Password: LOVETHIS4USKLOU95
